{"tid":910292,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"最好食嘅豬扒包","createTime":"2018-11-21T05:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T06:30:53.000Z","uid":135896,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6d621a25cbf4977ffe5fd6ec8daa57ce819ba15c","tid":910292,"uid":135896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"事先聲明你當我打手啦<br />\n<br />\n澳門嗰啲食極都頂唔住，又乾又硬又冇汁，食到胃抽筋<br />\n<br />\n老麥鋒味個吉列豬扒包真係得，塊豬扒吉列又有油，沙律醬加埋洋蔥勁match, 澳門嗰啲又硬豬仔包又乾身又冇汁冇剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39a9531250abad8f81da4b3b0e45b636c18cbf6","tid":910292,"uid":28493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T05:41:52.000Z","msg":"你成世仔係咪冇食過好食既野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df5736ae9564a299a17366daa82951f92c1e5a1","tid":910292,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T05:55:00.000Z","msg":"你唔識搵好食澳門豬扒包啫"},{"pid":"5da38a6a7e418884951f451b058acaa0b0d9538b","tid":910292,"uid":186379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"食左啦<br />\n食開垃圾先會話好食<br />\n豬扒無味 完全唔夠吉列 好似食緊塊豬柳咁<br />\n沙律醬蓋過哂洋蔥味<br />\n係食沙律醬定食洋蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫沙律醬豬柳bell啦 屌"},{"pid":"78f57d0ad2d03cc34171a3c34d9b51c8a07c1fde","tid":910292,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5da38a6a7e418884951f451b058acaa0b0d9538b","tid":910292,"uid":186379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"食左啦<br />\n食開垃圾先會話好食<br />\n豬扒無味 完全唔夠吉列 好似食緊塊豬柳咁<br />\n沙律醬蓋過哂洋蔥味<br />\n係食沙律醬定食洋蔥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫沙律醬豬柳bell啦 屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"洋蔥唔夠捻，垃圾"},{"pid":"312a5f7f7fd9f5c4e7f53c91bc3bbcfe8a5a9c2b","tid":910292,"uid":135896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:07:58.000Z","msg":"澳門有邊隻豬扒包唔係乾爭爭冇汁？我食咗五六次唔同地方，最後決定放棄以後都唔食<br />\n<br />\n老乜呢隻唔係有乜特別，只係正正常常加返醬汁，用吉列俾返啲油，已經好好食<br />\n<br />\n以前啲所謂地道豬扒包根本就無人食（係啲地踎小食店，個個都寧願食漢堡啊），佢10年八年前澳門吹番起"},{"pid":"5ef066fcd8ed916690d968d2439c76fe715edfb5","tid":910292,"uid":4052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:08:43.000Z","msg":"塊吉豬先離普，唔知似乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e125be315df7b0e8c401196bd0ffaadf82f9d00","tid":910292,"uid":48251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"吹奏大利來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乾到pk<br />\n<br />\n有間賣外賣豬排包反而唔錯"},{"pid":"7e4b5fb394c5a861474a9f62b46201fab7224492","tid":910292,"uid":191765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:23:54.000Z","msg":"丹麥餅店都夠打巢老麥啦"},{"pid":"41a6df6f45a124f09c5ece85333e251ca948f161","tid":910292,"uid":135896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e125be315df7b0e8c401196bd0ffaadf82f9d00","tid":910292,"uid":48251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"吹奏大利來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 乾到pk<br />\n<br />\n有間賣外賣豬排包反而唔錯"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:27:43.000Z","msg":"淨係睇圖我都覺得胃痛，一路咬啲麵包溝埋啲豬扒黐實晒係個口入邊，要飲好多水沖入個肚，真係唔知邊個天才發明，話好食嗰啲根本就痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9dc564051f25df39ee8ad468c9aa29f8c37e3d0","tid":910292,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T06:28:29.000Z","msg":"食鮑魚唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab82d979e81dea5dbab2b361c01e1bb48e6dd8f","tid":910292,"uid":48251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score